        "solutionCode": "def membership_status(is_member):\n    if not is_member:\n        return 'You need to sign up to access this feature'\n    else:\n        return 'Welcome back!'\n\nimport ast\n\ndef _parse_arg(raw):\n    try:\n        return ast.literal_eval(raw)\n    except Exception:\n        return raw\n\n_inputs = []\ntry:\n    while True:\n        _inputs.append(input())\nexcept EOFError:\n    pass\nis_member = _parse_arg(_inputs[0]) if len(_inputs) > 0 else \"\"\n\nprint(membership_status(is_member))"
      }
